* coders/wpg.c Crash on row overflow fixed oss-fuzz 7639 thanks to oss-fuzz.

The problem behind this crash is obvious:

 image->columns		1		unsigned long
 image->columns-3	4294967294	unsigned long

Condition can be modified:
    while(x < image->columns-3)
Fix:
    while(x+3 < image->columns)

For signed ints it would work fine. May be that the type image->columns changed someaday
from signed to unsigned.

